AI Career Path Recommender

## Project 3: AI Recommendation Logic

## 📖 Overview

The **AI Career Path Recommender** is a content-based recommendation system that helps users discover the most suitable career paths based on their technical skills. Using **TF-IDF vectorization** and **Cosine Similarity**, the system analyzes user skills and matches them with job roles from a comprehensive database.

This project demonstrates the fundamental principles of recommendation systems used by industry leaders like Netflix, Amazon, and LinkedIn.

