Mathematical Formulas
TF-IDF:

text
TF(t,d) = frequency of term t in document d
IDF(t) = log(N / df(t))
TF-IDF(t,d) = TF(t,d) × IDF(t)
Cosine Similarity:

text
cos(θ) = (Σ(Ai × Bi)) / (√ΣAi² × √ΣBi²)
